# NETWORK::NETWORK_SET_OVERRIDE_TUTORIAL_SESSION_CHAT

## Summary
Enables/disables

## Parameters
* **BOOL** override

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
By default, players in different tutorial sessions cannot chat. This allows that to be overridden.
